description:
Sweet Home Alabama - Season 4, Episode 7


The Bar Fight

It's a night out on the town for Kelsey and the few guys left standing. But what's supposed to be a fun evening takes a dramatic turn for the worse. A city guy attempts to show Kelsey what life would be like in the glamorous bright lights of his hometown. On the most emotional elimination night yet, more suitors are sent away.


Original Air Date: 27-Dec-2013




Sweet Home Alabama - Season 4, Episode 8


The Night Train

A romantic date unfolds on a freight train; Kelsey takes guys to the zoo for up-close encounter.


Original Air Date: 03-Jan-2014
